## ----------------------- MESSAGE  ------------------------------------  #
These repository contains all the training recipes for my previous research
work based on CURRENNT.

Note:
1. Training data cannot released in this repository. Please prepare the data 
   by yourself and change the configurations accordingly. 

2. Basic files, such as network.jsn, config.cfg, and log_train can be found.
   Unless special config.pm and config_syn.cfg are necessary, please use the
   default files in CURRENNT_scripts

3. Some of the log_train are generated by old CURRENNT versions. They may
   look different if the newest CURRENNT is used.

4. Please check each research work listed on tonywangx.github.io, and access 
   the training recipes through the link on that webpage